<br>
Cigarette companies now know their products are harmful. They now know they are addictive. They said they did not know this &quot;back when&quot;. But, of course they did.  They were caught lying, and are being made to pay for it.<br>
<br>
The question is, did/do Sony know EQ is harmful ? Did/do they purposefully manufacture (code), package and sell EQ so that it's addictive ? (As opposed to just marketing their product).<br>
